Troubleshooting Tips
WHOIS Lookup Failures:

Some domains use privacy protection services
Rate limiting may occur with bulk queries
Try different WHOIS servers with -h flag
crt.sh API Issues:

API may be slow or timeout with large result sets
Add retry logic with exponential backoff
Implement request delays (1-2 seconds between queries)
Python Library Errors:

Ensure all dependencies are installed: pip3 install python-whois requests
Use virtual environment to avoid conflicts
Check Python version compatibility (3.6+)
JSON Parsing Errors:

crt.sh may return empty responses for some domains
Validate JSON before parsing
Handle exceptions for malformed responses
